SYS(3050,1,VAL(SYS(1001)))
DO TBSAVE.PRG

SET DEFAULT TO W:\FOXAPPS\
OPEN DATABASE W:\FOXAPPS\SHORTDATA SHARED
 

** SET ESCAPE OFF **
** DISABLE EXIT HOTKEY **
ON KEY LABEL ESCAPE DO NOESCAPE 
ON KEY LABEL ALT+E DO NOEXIT 
ON KEY LABEL F1 DO NOEXIT


** SHOW ERROR MESSAGE ON ERRORS **
ON ERROR DO W:\FOXAPPS\SHRTRIDG\ERR_FIX

** SET DEFAULT SETTINGS **
SET EXCLUSIVE OFF
SET BELL OFF
SET TALK OFF

*!*	IF VERSION(5) = 600 
*!*		DEFINE WINDOW HIDECOM FROM 1,1 TO 3,3
*!*		ACTIVATE WINDOW COMMAND IN HIDECOM
*!*		DO BETSY.MPR
*!*		RETURN
*!*	ENDIF	
	

KEYBOARD '{ALT+H}'

DO SHRTRIDG\PRECHECK.MPR
*READ EVENTS

KEYBOARD '{ALT+H}'   

*SET SKIP OF PAD Hide OF _MSYSMENU .T.


PROCEDURE NOESCAPE
   ESCAPE=""
ENDPROC  

PROCEDURE NOEXIT
	RETURN
ENDPROC 
   
*KEYBOARD '{ALT+H}'   










